(1)
103 Circle Road, east side, between Redmond and New York Aves., showing the W.A. Tyler residence. The view is northeastward toward the Lower New York Bay.

August 1932.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, another view. The vantage point is the A.T. Pouch residence, at 120 Circle Road.

August 1932.

P. L. Sperr.
